Integrate **bake-off winners** into xf and cass (coding_agent_session_search). Both tools share the same semantic search infrastructure but serve different data:

- **xf**: X (Twitter) archive search - tweets, DMs, likes, bookmarks
- **cass**: Coding agent session search - Claude/GPT conversations, code, reasoning

This bead covers wiring the winning embedding/reranker models into the shared search pipeline.

