## What is cass?

**cass** (Coding Agent Session Search) is a companion CLI for searching AI coding session archives:

```
cass search "how to implement auth middleware"
cass search "that bug with async/await" --sessions last-week
cass search "refactoring discussion" --agent claude
```

It indexes:
- AI conversation transcripts (Claude, GPT, Codex)
- Code snippets from sessions
- Tool calls and reasoning traces
- Session metadata (duration, tokens, model)

cass shares the same Rust search engine as xf, so embedding/reranker improvements benefit both.

